items.content_text:
### Storage / [Google Developer Experts](https://developers.google.com/experts/all/technology/web-technologies)

*   [ngx-reactive-storage (‚≠ê52)](https://github.com/e-oz/ngx-reactive-storage) - Wrapper around IndexedDB and localStorage that allows you to create databases and tables using a simple, promise-based API. Changes to the data can be seen with Angular Signals or RxJS Observables.
*   [ng2-webstorage (‚≠ê428)](https://github.com/PillowPillow/ng2-webstorage) - LocalStorage and SessionStorage manager.
*   [angular-async-local-storage (‚≠ê676)](https://github.com/cyrilletuzi/angular-async-local-storage) - Efficient client-side storage for Angular: simple API + performance + Observables + validation.
